      "title": "Sri Lanka shares gain in mid-day trade",
      "author": "",
      "body_lines": [
        "ECONOMYNEXT \u2013 Sri Lanka\u2019s shares moved up in mid-day trade on Monday (01) continuing the positive momentum from the previous session, Colombo Stock Exchange data showed.",
        "The main All Share Price Index gained 0.83 percent or 63.86 points to 7,795 at 1130 hours.",
        "The most liquid index moved up 0.84 percent or 20.68 points to 2,469.",
        "Top gainers were Hayleys, Dipped Products and Malwatte Valley Plantations."
